    algorithmSteps: "1. prev = null, curr = head.\n2. While curr: lưu next = curr.next; curr.next = prev; prev = curr; curr = next.\n3. Return prev (head mới).\n4. Recursive: base null/1 node; reverse rest; head.next.next = head; head.next = null.",
    howItWorks: "Iterative lật từng mũi tên một. Mỗi bước curr trỏ ngược về prev. Cuối cùng prev ở node cuối cũ.",
    dryRun: "1→2→3→null\n\nprev=null, curr=1: 1→null, prev=1, curr=2\nprev=1, curr=2: 2→1→null, prev=2, curr=3\nprev=2, curr=3: 3→2→1→null, prev=3, curr=null\nreturn 3",
    visualization: "Before: 1→2→3→null\nStep:   null←1  2→3\nAfter:  3→2→1→null",
    codePattern: "export function reverseLinkedList(head) {\n  let prev = null, curr = head;\n  while (curr) {\n    const next = curr.next;\n    curr.next = prev;\n    prev = curr;\n    curr = next;\n  }\n  return prev;\n}",
    bigO: "Time O(n), Space O(1) iterative; O(n) stack recursive.",
    bigOWhy: "Duyệt mỗi node 1 lần. Iterative chỉ 3 con trỏ. Recursive: n stack frames.",
    commonMistakes: "- Mất next trước khi gán curr.next = prev.\n- Return head cũ thay vì prev.\n- Recursive: quên head.next = null → cycle.",
    compareApproaches: "Iterative O(1) space — preferred interview. Recursive elegant nhưng stack O(n). Dùng stack push all rồi pop — O(n) space, không cần pointer skill.",
    interviewTips: "- Viết iterative trước, offer recursive.\n- Vẽ 3 con trỏ trên giấy.\n- Follow-up: reverse between m and n.",
